    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
    <b>Description:</b> <br>
    This is the mother of all direct damage spells! The most powerful direct damage spell in the game. It does around 1100 Damage. One major drawback is that to get to two runes you will need to be in a group of 15+ level 50's. One rune, The rune of Frost comes off a level 50+ Dragon named Lord Nagafen. The other rune, I dont know but I assume it is just as hard. Currently as of 7/15/99, there is only one wizard that has Ice Coment. That is becuase Lord Nagafen has only been killed once.<BR><EM>Need mana info</EM><BR>
<BR>
<B>Research:</B><BR>Rune of Frost, Rune of Astral<br>
    <b>Effects:</b><br>
    Direct Damage
    </font>
    
