			When you get the quest, you recieve a book that tells where to find the spokes (in riddles) and a box to carry and combine them. Myself and my Wizard friend 'accidentally' found one of the spokes last night and are renewing efforts to retrieve all of the spokes. They are scattered all across Norrath. And from what we can figure out, they are in places suitible for anywhere from level 15 up. Undoubtedly many of you have already seen a spoke but didn't know it. The one we found (before identify) looked like an orange fork and said it was &quot;A Rod&quot; with a weight of 0.01. Happy hunting!
